        <h1>Welcome</h1>
        <p class="lead">The Need-To-Know Changes in the City of Milwaukee's Garbage Collections.</p>
          <p>New garbage and recycling schedules are now in effect beginning January 1, 2017 through December 31, 2018.  
            Residents must roll their garbage and recycling carts to the curb by 7:00 a.m. on the designated collection day.  
            Sanitation crews will not collect the carts from their storage areas.</p>
